                    text: "[b]Children's Privacy[\b]\nOur Service does not address anyone under the age of 18 (\"Children\").We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 18. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your Children has provided us with Personal Data, please contact us. If we become aware that we have collected Personal Data from children without verification of parental consent, we take steps to remove that information from our servers.\n[b]Changes To This Privacy Policy[\b]\nWe may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.We will let you know via email and/or a prominent notice on our Service, prior to the change becoming effective and update the \"effective date\" at the top of this Privacy Policy.\nYou are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.[b]Contact Us[\b]\nIf you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:\n* By email: mlyangzon@up.edu.ph"
